        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Securing Our Schools Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to develop a strategy for securing elementary schools, secondary schools, and institutions of higher education from homeland security threats.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
